{"tid":737810,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"17歲少女未拍過拖向朱千雪求助，千雪BB霸氣回：未拍過拖唔係一件唔好嘅事！","createTime":"2018-07-11T05:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T13:41:21.000Z","uid":1886,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ec0329b869c9e2ee86e9aef45f786e1730b56111","tid":737810,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:41:15.000Z","msg":"前港姐朱千雪同岑杏賢係好姊妹，仲一齊主持節目《心理急救室》為少男少女解決煩惱。Big Big Channel專頁上載咗一段短片，內容關於一位17歲嘅少女因為驚自己冇拖拍而向兩位靚女求助<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，千雪即化身做「Miss Chu」教路，過程中仲爆出唔少金句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！ <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180709/photo/bkn-20180709220017573-0709_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180709220415\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180709%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180709220017573-0709_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180709220415&h=978da68e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n片段開始嘅時候，岑杏賢就話：「佢係一個準備升中六嘅17歲女仔，見身邊好多同學開始拍拖，自己仍然係A0<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （Available 0）。」呢個時候，Miss Chu即刻解釋「A0」係點解，即係單身兼未拍過拖，之後Miss Chu一臉認真話：「我覺得未拍過拖唔係一件唔好嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我唔理解亦唔認同呢種年輕人嘅心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，你結婚都係揀一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，完全唔覺得之前拍過十次拖係叻啲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，你話10A就叻啲啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180709/bkn-20180709220017573-0709_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180709%2Fbkn-20180709220017573-0709_00862_001.html&d=%2Fkaltkj%2F2%2BdPrSqMvx58uRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=b6cb8d10\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180709/bkn-20180709220017573-0709_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"63ec2025f7cb137c4f72989b3275e857b7b693e3","tid":737810,"uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:41:32.000Z","msg":"之後Miss Chu繼續金句王上身：「以前嘅年代啲人係好鍾意啲冇拍過拖嘅女仔，17歲未拍過拖驚咩？有個28歲未拍過嘅都唔驚啦，你驚咩？女仔拍拖quota（配額）唔多，我唔會因為要Experience（經歷拍拖）而去嘥呢樣嘢。」岑杏賢亦表示：「其實佢講個重點出嚟，係想有人關心同錫佢，其實有父母錫都係被愛緊。」最後Miss Chu總結：「唔好受社會壓力影響，唔好覺得呢樣（拍拖）係需求。」"},{"pid":"3c7d0859bd84c2c432ce03a278a4da75c3673515","tid":737810,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T06:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b036f51fd3151edd91d22c194afb96db0f87ee7","tid":737810,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T06:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a72c9f3566f45af227c5bc01d2a9254864c0f2","tid":737810,"uid":167791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T06:15:58.000Z","msg":"想知邊個28歲都未過拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64dc0e8673fd55afc84dbeedfab011296cbbf31b","tid":737810,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T13:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}